        <rdfs:comment>An entity holding detailed information about the available bed types, e.g. the quantity of twin beds for a hotel room. For the single case of just one bed of a certain type, you can use bed directly with a text. See also &lt;a class=&quot;localLink&quot; href=&quot;http://schema.org/BedType&quot;&gt;BedType&lt;/a&gt; (under development).</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:label>BedDetails</rdfs:label>
    </Class>
    


