        <rdfs:comment>A &lt;a class=&quot;localLink&quot; href=&quot;http://schema.org/FAQPage&quot;&gt;FAQPage&lt;/a&gt; is a &lt;a class=&quot;localLink&quot; href=&quot;http://schema.org/WebPage&quot;&gt;WebPage&lt;/a&gt; presenting one or more &quot;&lt;a href=&quot;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/FAQ&quot;&gt;Frequently asked questions&lt;/a&gt;&quot; (see also &lt;a class=&quot;localLink&quot; href=&quot;http://schema.org/QAPage&quot;&gt;QAPage&lt;/a&gt;).</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:label>FAQPage</rdfs:label>
    </Class>
    


