&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;localLink&quot; href=&quot;http://schema.org/ReceiveAction&quot;&gt;ReceiveAction&lt;/a&gt;: Unlike ReceiveAction, TakeAction implies that ownership has been transfered.&lt;/li&gt;
