        <schema1:rangeIncludes rdf:resource="http://schema.org/Number"/>
        <schema1:rangeIncludes rdf:resource="http://schema.org/Text"/>
        <rdfs:comment>The highest price of all offers available.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;

Usage guidelines:&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use values from 0123456789 (Unicode &apos;DIGIT ZERO&apos; (U+0030) to &apos;DIGIT NINE&apos; (U+0039)) rather than superficially similiar Unicode symbols.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use &apos;.&apos; (Unicode &apos;FULL STOP&apos; (U+002E)) rather than &apos;,&apos; to indicate a decimal point. Avoid using these symbols as a readability separator.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:label>highPrice</rdfs:label>
    </rdf:Description>
